sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant KB as Knowledge base
  participant DR as One driver
  participant MB as Morphological box
  participant CIB as CIB panel
  participant FLD as Scenario field
  participant AR as Archetypes

  Note over KB: ~70 sources, 3,905 chunks
  KB->>DR: extract + ground (keeps source_chunk_ids)
  Note over DR: 1 of 14 selected factors
  DR->>MB: 4 manifestations (optimistic to pessimistic)
  MB->>CIB: how does this factor couple to the others?
  Note over CIB: 5 personas, dissent preserved
  CIB-->>MB: 182 pairwise scores (-3 to +3)
  MB->>FLD: sample 4^14 = 268,435,456, keep 120 consistent
  FLD->>AR: HDBSCAN on ordinal encoding
  AR-->>AR: 5 named archetypes + ~40 continuum
  Note over KB,AR: every step traces back to source chunks
